          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Veterans Service Organization Modernization Act of 2021 </strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Housing and Urban Development to provide competitive grants to veterans service organizations for repairs or rehabilitation of existing facilities and for modernization of technologies. </p>]]>
        </text>
